      "message": "Prior to https://gn-review.googlesource.com/c/gn/+/20480, there\u0027s only one usage of MD5 in GN and it\u0027s for legacy compatibility with VS.\n\nLet\u0027s fix this now before it\u0027s impossible to change. I understand it\u0027s not security-critical, but let\u0027s not force people to import insecure hashes just to interoperate either :)",
